Developing a portal for a logistics management company. The company owns many delivery trucks.
On the home page of the portal we can be able to see a list of all free trucks and assigned trucks. 
From this page, we can also click a button to mark a truck as assigned to a task. 
Once assigned to a task, it is longer visible on the free trucks page.

there is another page that displays all the trucks currently delivering a task. 
On this page we can also able to mark the task as completed and send the truck back to the free trucks page.

Only authenticated warehouse managers with a username and password is able to access this portal 
